{"tid":1612124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《打機攻略》水魔法只適用於敵方防守狀態","createTime":"2019-10-02T07:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:49:15.000Z","uid":72792,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3100adf9818975714c214c088a7d3bc85b60ef84","tid":1612124,"uid":72792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"玩online game時好多人問點解無出水系魔法<br />\n最大限制係：<br />\n1）班怪物而家好少<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>一排過企定定</strong></span>比你掉<br />\n2）對方一出就係<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">速度系怪物</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，第一反應一定係避開對方攻擊<br />\n<br />\n導致唔少水魔法最後係準備左但無用到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我有少少建議，可以提高返水魔法既使用率</span></span><br />\n<strong>通常圍敵方基地個時，基地都係重防狀態<br />\n一堆怪物會on居居企係2m高既牆後面<br />\n仲有一兩個怪物企係哨位</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果大家係呢d時候<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">快閃玩水魔法</span></span><br />\n除左殺對方個措手不及<br />\n如果你係水魔法入面咩原材料都加<br />\n怪物一定會暫時退落黎睇下係咩<br />\n如果係<span style=\"color: red;\">助燃物料</span>就最好唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算係🎨遮左佢地視線，都可以減低佢地士氣<br />\n<br />\n大家成日屌圍基地無用<br />\n咁就比d攻略大家玩啦<br />\n希望可以提高水魔法既使用率<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">愈多人用，隊友就愈安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e9386f606efa2ac9687fa222e318955520205013","tid":1612124,"uid":72792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"琴日打機見到多左人轉職架啦<br />\n不過可以用魔法既時機唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35681aadad671e34a817416972648b00a8db267e","tid":1612124,"uid":72792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ef1ec18e62924cc8768516bcf87c4942de199323","tid":1612124,"uid":72792,"like":0,"d